        "subject": "LU-11373 libcfs: fix wrong check in libcfs_debug_vmsg2()",
        "message": "LU-11373 libcfs: fix wrong check in libcfs_debug_vmsg2()\n\nLogic here is we skip output if time is before @cdls_next\nreach and increase @cdls_count. however we did it in the\nopposite way, we will never skip any messages, because every\ntime we come in, @cdls_next wil be updated and @cdls_count\nwill be kept as zero forever.\n\nFixes: fdb5d3d50\nTest-parameters: trivial\nChange-Id: I5df7b81c49793bd7c3f63aca07e9663a83ffb2d7\nSigned-off-by: Wang Shilong <wshilong@ddn.com>\n"
      },
